_sText:
A map with all of your favorite disney princesses. The map is split up into each movie which includes Sleeping Beauty, Cinderella, Little Mermaid, Beauty and the Beast, Aladdin, Frog Princess and Snow White.

The map contains 40 CT spawns and 2 Terrorist spawns. 25 Pushable traps, and 2 non-pushable. 3 Secret nades, and 4 special endings.

Made for steamgamers.com deathrun, 66.150.121.71:27015.
